{"tid":1235993,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"【個人資料劫匪天堂】外國人在港的求醫記錄","createTime":"2019-06-17T10:09:40.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-17T10:10:41.000Z","uid":85252,"like":11,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"cc45edba8d1ad6902d2c8c152d9df2a73eb6cdd6","tid":1235993,"uid":85252,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-17T10:09:40.000Z","msg":"請問本地外藉人士的病歷是否都可以被警方透過醫管局直接獲得﹖<br />\n<br />\n英國領事館會否關注一下英國居民的病歷會否被不正確取用﹖又有冇違反歐盟嘅個人資料法例﹖<br />\n<br />\n我地唔可以令香港變成<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">個人資料劫匪天堂</span></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"93c2e87c5efa0d02e0bcd53ebca9c8987141e1e6","tid":1235993,"uid":156592,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-17T10:10:41.000Z","msg":"呢個可以係真建制派嘅政綱之一<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}